title: 065 - Alison Brie Larson
description: On today's show, the boys address the elephant in the room from yesterday's episode of The Pat McAfee Show, then try to do their best to move it forward and have a feel good Friday. They discuss Connor going to a special Dave Chappelle show the other night in Ohio, which TV show character they would like to put into a different show, what they've been watching on Netflix, and several other things in a packed folder of death. Don't forget to send your questions in @ThePodPMI on Twitter and Instagram. Stay safe out there, and have a good weekend. Enjoy.
